{"tid":1839222,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"2019年，香港人，平均每隔17日，就會返1次中國大陸","createTime":"2020-01-24T10:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T11:09:59.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cb54e7065753ae909c9d61ad939b477140f5909a","tid":1839222,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:19:05.000Z","msg":"中國國家移民管理局統計數據顯示，檢查出入境交通運輸工具3623.5萬輛(架、列、艘)次，同比增長3.4%。全年，內地居民出入境3.5億人次，<strong>香港</strong>、澳門、台灣居民<strong>來往內地(大陸)</strong>分別為<strong>1.6億</strong>、5358.7萬、1227.8萬人次，外國人入出境9767.5萬人次。<br />\n<br />\n1.6億人次 &divide; 750萬人<br />\n= 21.3次<br />\n平均每位香港人，去大陸21.3次<br />\n<br />\n365日/21次<br />\n= 17.1日<br />\n即係每個香港人，平均每隔2星期半，就會返一次支那"},{"pid":"240b3d694ce3be4b304084116f5f7647235e0645","tid":1839222,"uid":312242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:19:36.000Z","msg":"&quot;香港&quot;人"},{"pid":"82e5dffa636b5852398f45b3c1bf2ca1211e7520","tid":1839222,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cb54e7065753ae909c9d61ad939b477140f5909a","tid":1839222,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:19:05.000Z","msg":"中國國家移民管理局統計數據顯示，檢查出入境交通運輸工具3623.5萬輛(架、列、艘)次，同比增長3.4%。全年，內地居民出入境3.5億人次，<strong>香港</strong>、澳門、台灣居民<strong>來往內地(大陸)</strong>分別為<strong>1.6億</strong>、5358.7萬、1227.8萬人次，外國人入出境9767.5萬人次。<br />\n<br />\n1.6億人次 &divide; 750萬人<br />\n= 21.3次<br />\n平均每位香港人，去大陸21.3次<br />\n<br />\n365日/21次<br />\n= 17.1日<br />\n即係每個香港人，平均每隔2星期半，就會返一次支那"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T10:20:21.000Z","msg":"資料來源<a href=\"https://m.chinanews.com/wap/detail/zw/kong/2020/01-05/9051628.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.chinanews.com%2Fwap%2Fdetail%2Fzw%2Fkong%2F2020%2F01-05%2F9051628.shtml&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77VuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=d796c627\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.chinanews.com/wap/detail/zw/kong/2020/01-05/9051628.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"4185830518a1817e63af6dce7286f333464b